{"tid":295823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港獨只是口號 萬般皆下品 惟有收錢高","createTime":"2017-06-24T05:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T06:06:36.000Z","uid":59565,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05f8a9dcbef50bd7addd9f729a9146c17bcfa203","tid":295823,"uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:14:49.000Z","msg":"說穿了 根本所有問題都係錢<br />\n<br />\n黑警：毅進星加國力書院，只有當差先有咁上下人工<br />\n共產黨：只有收翻香港，高官嘅資產同黑錢先有保障<br />\n支聯會：口喊平反六四，就可以每年籌款<br />\n金鐘商戶：我係藍絲，因為佔中會影響生意<br />\n連登仔（部份）：我愛國！因為有二千蚊收<br />\n廢青：我支持港獨！因為獨立後先有機會向上流動搵錢<br />\n<br />\n其實港獨 民主 同埋愛國愛黨都係不過係一句口號啫<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/131342_f09595438df0f351f5c3874e81f8c1f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F131342_f09595438df0f351f5c3874e81f8c1f1.jpg&h=aacbae1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申獨派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1249809d3473de56b71c4a781b8a764113a833","tid":295823,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:16:26.000Z","msg":"係，香港最燒錢既就係基建，地產，以上相比只係散紙"},{"pid":"dbef23deb5eda8ea0ccaa27f0c516e598e3e5933","tid":295823,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"利益衝突"},{"pid":"5ec11c463cce5c01f6d717511332d55d8fb7236f","tid":295823,"uid":59565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"港獨要成功 第一步一定先集資 搵金主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c333cebd4e6a47aa530c424f5dbab5f2bec700","tid":295823,"uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔 1200蚊就買得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\